{"tid":1632631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議新職業：和理歸！送啲平民番屋企","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T20:17:52.000Z","uid":293005,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9314ab6914be8a794cd83f85789ca6914aff2b","tid":1632631,"uid":293005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:07:36.000Z","msg":"（第一次開post，屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n話說呢兩三日黨鐵都收皮，大家出黎行動巴士都會停駛或改道，地圖亦愈開愈闊。都真係有好多平民或者外國人係收唔到資訊，唔知點番屋企，當中都不乏淺黃或者潛在支持者。無謂送佢俾對家／免佢受紅VAN 的士劏客之苦，順便解釋手足行動原因。<br />\n<br />\n（利申：真係有被唔少外國人問路，發生咩事，或見到老人家等好耐都唔知巴士會唔會黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n有無可能新增職業：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理歸</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n風險似乎比接放學細一啲，接送啲有需要嘅平民、老人家、外國人，僱工姐姐，減少佢地對前線嘅負面諗法。<br />\n<br />\n認同請幫推，Ｐ牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f997184b0a4df4ff929c09651470f31deb3d7c5d","tid":1632631,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:07:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be0b96db2af29983476f15c0a1366ea2ff4459be","tid":1632631,"uid":143319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:08:43.000Z","msg":"好提議 我地要不斷進化<br />\n幫你推"},{"pid":"2db0243457fb82191decd6d2bb8a3b1479de0b7a","tid":1632631,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:09:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b7d9f15027160fd5348b3c91005922e7dcd20bf","tid":1632631,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:10:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a544495ac05149ecb8b25ccedf7c08b17b7a3b1","tid":1632631,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:10:29.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e529a088aa01f2e6b7338ecd8416c47a9b8bb23","tid":1632631,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:10:31.000Z","msg":"解決鬼問題 送完人咁送人個d點算"},{"pid":"65c93694fee7ce84f7fbb64eca22072ec01f1206","tid":1632631,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:12:04.000Z","msg":"文宣呼籲唔敢示威/早左既人落街掩護手足番歸"},{"pid":"a3dbac3b1c851d0cc804923cc0c630bfcc0bce10","tid":1632631,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"出錢包架旅遊巴得唔得, 當然司機要自己人"},{"pid":"ccce48f963ea309ad02e130a78f4f93fb15e0cc3","tid":1632631,"uid":114245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:17:56.000Z","msg":"要諗埋送果個人點走喎"},{"pid":"2cc7357930228ef845a3f4b9ae82aacdbb274418","tid":1632631,"uid":228203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:21:57.000Z","msg":"呢個真係有效，但係最好著翻黑衫先做，咁先有宣傳效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個上司全家藍底，但係佢個外母之前係中環蕩失路，又無車走，之後有手足叫校巴免費送佢翻屋企，聽個上司講佢外母依家周圍同人講黑衫好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一單係淺藍同事之前係旺角中tg暈咗係馬路，比手足救翻，幫佢用水洗面，送佢去醫院。依家變咗淺黃，成日係公司屌班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338a02ad62d194e019800ccb801f6f2f393fec12","tid":1632631,"uid":158426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:22:01.000Z","msg":"同意 前日送左一堆阿姨有大有細 絕對有助穩定民心"},{"pid":"3b2d42563ffe53335c76b07f70c2b335111797a8","tid":1632631,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"有得諗"},{"pid":"ffc13ffa0c05c43bd93b235a8f4d2134ec1f66a8","tid":1632631,"uid":293005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:26:45.000Z","msg":"安全問題都要諗，可能真係最初目標係啲老人家，外國人，比較無咁容易有後果，車完咪走，或者區內兜啲短程<br />\n<br />\n但最緊要係呢個係和理非職業，即係對家都車，純為幫大家喺無交通情況下番屋企，我自己覺得同接放學比都係風險低啲"},{"pid":"207ee2c22550e520efeca1b2aae64ca6e6a41702","tid":1632631,"uid":293005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be0b96db2af29983476f15c0a1366ea2ff4459be","tid":1632631,"uid":143319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:08:43.000Z","msg":"好提議 我地要不斷進化<br />\n幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:29:35.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5910a23b2b3ee8f6e3058ef3a48b568e4ea12ba","tid":1632631,"uid":47149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aed377313c5e6e8d46a980932d85add1ac0860e","tid":1632631,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3e4c9f36d76d85335a9d0ecc0485ecf188a11f","tid":1632631,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:55:12.000Z","msg":"好似幾好，不過會唔會爭左校巴資源"},{"pid":"24f55a2c6554d3267543f25be75fa7d47a4c9218","tid":1632631,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:59:31.000Z","msg":"今日走咗成10轉<br />\n就係車啲返唔到屋企嘅阿姐同工人<br />\n<br />\n其中一個係響旺角段荔橋快線見到有個中年阿姨響度行<br />\n嗰度啲車好撚高速 嚇親我即刻捉佢上車送佢返屋企<br />\n<br />\n佢上車淨係識講唔該唔該....<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企附近見到兩個賓賓姐姐<br />\n同的士司機傾左好耐都上唔到車<br />\n其中一個係住我樓上 一見到我就喊.....<br />\n之後又車埋佢返屋企......."},{"pid":"2a29cd50b719182b1e0d204d2344b1dad0eacd93","tid":1632631,"uid":293005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b3e4c9f36d76d85335a9d0ecc0485ecf188a11f","tid":1632631,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:55:12.000Z","msg":"